Homework 2. Flask.
-----------------

1. Return information from requirements.txt
   PATH: /requirements/ 
  
2. Display  100 or a specified number of generated users and their emails.
   Ex.: 'Dmytro aasdasda@mail.com'.
   PATH: /generate-users/<int:users_number>
   For generating names: https://pypi.org/project/Faker/ 

3. Return mean height and weight from hw.csv.
   Ex.: Mean height: 192cm; Mean weight: 85kg.
   PATH: /mean/
   File hw.csv in folder files/

4. Display number of cosmonauts in the space at the moment.
   Use http://api.open-notify.org/astros.json, https://pypi.org/project/requests/
   PATH: /space/

!!! Do all tasks in the separated branch, create pull request and then merge with main.

-----------------

hw2_flask_maim.py - web application based on Flask

Folders:
files/ for hw.csv
static/ for style.css
templates/ for html templates
         base.html - base templates
         entry.html - main page
         requirements.html - templates for task 1.
         generate_users.html - templates for task 2.
         mean.html - templates for task 3.
         space.html - templates for task 4.


